QuestData.Title: Proof of Strength: Gronn Eye
QuestData.Description: This eye is proof of your strength at slaying ogron and your gladiator friend has born witness!$b$bTake the eye back to Jonaa and claim your accolades!
QuestData.LogDescription: Take the proof to Rangari Jonaa at Highpass in Gorgrond.
QuestData.RewardText: A gronn's eye is not something they part with alive. Your gladiator described a fight hard won and this trophy is a testament to your abilities. Well done!
